'''''The Book of the Homeless''''' is a [[1916 in literature|1916]] collection of [[essay]]s, [[art]], [[poetry]], and [[Sheet music|musical scores]]. Proceeds of its sales were used to fund [[Displaced person|civilians displaced]] by [[World War I]]. It was edited by [[Edith Wharton]].
